# Root SRC for the transforms showcase monorepo.
#
# This example now EVALUATES and statically validates end to end:
#   capyfun check --root examples/transforms
# The transform and agent tool builtins (replace/move/copy/rewrite_message,
# apply_patch, agent_transform/template, and the harness/model/agent/
# prompt_template rules) are implemented (T1-T4). Structural transforms also
# apply during `capyfun import`. The remaining piece is generative execution
# (T5): actually running an agent_transform and materializing its output to a
# content-addressed patch. See docs/design/transformations.md.

monorepo(
    name = "tinytree",
    default_branch = "main",
)
